data.description:
This beautiful house has 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms an open concept floorplan with split bedrooms. The beautiful big open kitchen features a breakfast bar, stainless-steel appliances including, range, microwave, dishwasher and refrigerator won't disappoint, perfect for gathering and entertaining.
Enjoy a great dinner in the dining room overlooking the backyard through the big bay windows. Large covered patio to enjoy those cooler fall evenings. Great size backyard for your kids to play or to start gardening, storage shed will convey.
